# Print the star Pattern
# Take a int input of maximum rows from user. And take one bool value from user in forn of 0 and 1.
# if user input 1 -> True, then print the below pattern
*
**
***
****....
# else at input 0 -> False, Print reverse Pattern

#CODE
# CODE-URL: https://ide.geeksforgeeks.org/KlA0Xkp8TM

#code
n = int(input("\nenter the rows you want in pattern"))

b = int(input("\nenter 1 for straight pattern and 0 for reverse"))
b = bool(b)
print(b)

if(b == True):
    for i in range(n+1):
        for j in range(i):
            print("*",end="")
        print(" ")
        
else:
    for i in range(n,0,-1):
        for j in range(1,i+1):
            print("*",end="")
        print(" ")


